ee kings of Scotland, notably  Robert the Bruce  (  1274–1329 ), who freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert LeMegre was born about 1142, in France. She had at least 1 son with Robert LeMegre."},"et":{"about 1142–":"umbes 1142–Surnud","1142–Male":"1142–Surnud","1167–Male":"1167–Surnud","1142–Female":"1142–Surnud","1167":"1167","1142":"1142","about 1167":"umbes 1167","about 1142":"umbes 1142","England":"England","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1142–":"noin 1142–Kuollut","1142–Male":"1142–Kuollut","1167–Male":"1167–Kuollut","1142–Female":"1142–Kuollut","1167":"1167","1142":"1142","about 1167":"noin 1167","about 1142":"noin 1142","England":"England","France":"Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1142–":"environ 1142–Décédée","1142–Male":"1142–Décédé","1167–Male":"1167–Décédé","1142–Female":"1142–Décédée","1167":"1167","1142":"1142","about 1167":"environ 1167","about 1142":"environ 1142","England":"Angleterre","France":"France","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert LeMegre est née environ 1142, à France. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Robert LeMegre."},"de":{"about 1142–":"um 1142–Verstorben","1142–Male":"1142–Verstorben","1167–Male":"1167–Verstorben","1142–Female":"1142–Verstorben","1167":"1167","1142":"1142","about 1167":"um 1167","about 1142":"um 1142","England":"England","France":"Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert LeMegre wurde um 1142 in Frankreich geboren. Sie hatte mit Robert LeMegre mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"about 1142–":"about 1142–Desede","1142–Male":"1142–Desede","1167–Male":"1167–Desede","1142–Female":"1142–Desede","1167":"1167","1142":"1142","about 1167":"about 1167","about 1142":"about 1142","England":"England","France":"France"},"hu":{"about 1142–":"1142 körül–elhunyt","1142–Male":"1142–elhunyt","1167–Male":"1167–elhunyt","1142–Female":"1142–elhunyt","1